                "Literal": {
                  "Value": "'Overall progress is calculated by counting the number of ''Completed'' activities and comparing this count against the total number of scheduled activities, excluding Milestones, WBS Summaries and Level of Effort items. This performance is visualised by two accompanying charts that show the count of activities by their ''Actual Finish'' dates across the project''s duration. These charts compare actual performance against the baseline''s ''Early Finish'' and ''Late Finish'' activity counts by date, while also displaying the current distribution for those metrics to provide a count-based view of schedule performance.'"
